Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:29.27,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}决心不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:31.74,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.81,0:22:34.95,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\be1}都能重新起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:48.58,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}轻飘飘地随风飘扬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.71,0:22:52.76,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}飒爽而来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.82,0:22:56.58,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}若只想消磨时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.59,0:23:00.48,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}就给我认真点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:03.38,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}黑白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:08.18,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你应该也早已厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:12.04,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}被弄脏也不会放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.13,0:23:18.54,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}紧拥着唯一的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:20.48,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}梦想不会就此终结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:22.18,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}你依然保持本色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:26.37,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}随时都可以重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:30.99,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}摄人心魄的疯狂刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:34.16,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}才能拯救爱 woo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:36.30,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}决心不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:37.92,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}谁也无法破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:42.29,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}给人添麻烦又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:44.10,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}想要继续呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:46.49,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:49.74,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}都能重新起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.98,0:23:54.61,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}「想要的只是时代的一页」
