Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:05.63,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,200)\blur4}遍地的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:10.61,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}升空的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:15.17,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}数亿的生息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:23.06,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur4}此刻 世界转世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是迈克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我叫迈克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年迈克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这装束 这发色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近从未见过…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚在海原上疯狂作乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼大王的化身？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从遥远的地方而来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 迈克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在恋爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫克瑞丝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识她？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能看见她？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想来告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.93,0:01:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然是关于她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1600)}以及这艘船的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳光下金色的长发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克瑞丝是位美丽的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是位命运多舛的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为普通人 看不见克瑞丝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不用说触碰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等绝望的境遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是克瑞丝 并不孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问为何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她遇见了科伦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得见我在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副眼镜的度数准确无误
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有常人没有的生命气息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那气息的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫科伦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青年科伦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫克瑞丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独的克瑞丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的人 看不见你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看见我的男性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上最幸福的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 如此可爱的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科伦纳…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始 克瑞丝属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克瑞丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体犹如蜃景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看见我 已是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但无法触碰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请忘记今天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再出现在你面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克瑞丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 克瑞丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无法触碰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已经邂逅了你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却说再也看不见这笑容了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这么让人悲伤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后的每一个晨与夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都希望有你的笑容相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是非分之想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 科伦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我成为世上最幸福的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是为了这一刻而降生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么硕大的宝石 从没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满脸幸福啊 科伦纳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全城的酒吧里 都在议论你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你和一个不存在的梦中情人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过着卿卿我我的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人看不见她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必理睬那些碎言碎語
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错 酒后失言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才路过你家时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺道问候她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:05:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清纯的水手服 栗色的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如丝般的长发 熠熠生辉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真让人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没对任何人提起过克瑞丝的打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 你也看得见她？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也拥有生命气息之光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拥有的不是气息之光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔法眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着这么危险的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个男人都随身带着一把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见却摸不着的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎熬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有她的笑容就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的头发真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你手指上缠着的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是克瑞丝的头发？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！绝不可能认错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这确实是克瑞丝的金发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是居住在北海的魔女艾茵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我胸前的是夜之宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要带着它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以触摸到克瑞丝的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最明白它的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以握住克瑞丝的小手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拥抱她的胴体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲吻她的朱唇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的话 给你也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 不能白给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！ 不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以触摸到她的身体？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要能见到克瑞丝的笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是女人 最清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克瑞丝想被你抱在怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天晚上都在梦中流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,储蓄…股票…国债…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把古董收藏放到网上变卖…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换宝石的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的东西只须一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北岛的造船厂里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要启动那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗 用那艘船交换这颗宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还有本土来的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快 要到下一幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科伦纳开动了船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那竟然是一艘飞天之船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沉醉于驾驭飞船的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如我心中所想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能自由自在地翱翔蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:08:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已不再是过去的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科伦纳驾驶这艘船周游世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是鱼星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞天是禁忌之事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡高塔上居住着女王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近女王的房间是禁忌的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就连飞鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被禁止飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂鲨鱼 喂鲨鱼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都去喂鲨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这颗鱼星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统治者必须身在最高处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所在的这个高度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我所独有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不识趣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都去喂鲨鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鱼星球的新王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的戏份只有这么少…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 王必须在至高之处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:08:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到达最高处的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是王！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科伦纳成了鱼星球的王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么克瑞丝呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘坐飞船在星球上自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐冲淡了科伦纳对克瑞丝的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦或者是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的他已经失去了看见克瑞丝的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 科伦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样也无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜失去你真正的幸福 克瑞丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟想去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这艘船就足够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上的一切都已归我所有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有言在先船得归我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是我的船了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的船？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没察觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成船本身了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是船本身…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说…我变成了船？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由夜间飞行剧团表演的「神话前夜」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入中场休息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15分钟后上演下半场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要一口气看完哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 班长同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人他们的表演如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还算耐人寻味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事感觉好悲情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来科伦纳抛弃爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择了野心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 酷酷的班长同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是蛮赞同现实派的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便那样 克瑞丝也是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌 很好听
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本土来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了看这场演出特意…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更准确地说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了看你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君喜欢上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎样的女孩子 想来看看
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科伦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,履行诺言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出这艘船…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 魔女不会害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于出现了 魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是这星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有最大魔力的船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七千年来我一直在等待它的苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜了 在我的魔法下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定把这颗夜之宝石给你是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你也没想着抱得美人归了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾茵…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么可以动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被我的魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这艘船拥有星球上最大的魔力」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我和它一体化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有比你更多的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用了这艘船的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你马上就会和船完全一体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是抛弃所爱少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科伦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾茵～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与船一体化后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科伦纳不再会衰老也不会死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他仍旧做着鱼星球的王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位王深居塔内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不露面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科伦纳的船还保留着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有巨大魔力的船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无人能够破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 只有施以封印
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克瑞丝的过去竟然有过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么告诉我这样的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非 你也是魔女？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那个乌贼大王的化身？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是「熵族」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不使用魔力的族人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你亦如昔时的科伦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拥有生命气息之光的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能够看见克瑞丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 可以驱动那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 生命气息之光的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们「熵族」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是决不使用魔力的银河一族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否破坏那艘拥有强大魔力的船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及偶遇船的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些生灵们的生杀大权
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不属于我们掌管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论你如何处置那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都只能在一旁守望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上应该吻戏了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来没这段台词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长的临场发挥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让你至少知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这艘船的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样可以驱动船的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后做何选择
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也像科伦纳那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着一把刀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有生命气息之光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一定不是让我用来开动船的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是让我看到她的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有一把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是为保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承诺 克瑞丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:18:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会守护你心目中最珍贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次公演也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这出戏是你写的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束得真及时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及时…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到迈克被船的魔力控制
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克瑞丝又会伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这取决于观众的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是中学时代的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈田晴菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君总是提到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那么常提到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 已经见过面了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚来我们家住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还赶得上末班渡船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我送你去港口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用不用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有完工宴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君 比以前还开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说 感觉闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也听得见世界的声音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君初恋的佳人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我完全不同的类型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 完全不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也是个好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的联系方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有某种与众不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 做我的模特好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 老爸没教育好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球的命运终于要取决于他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同于其他的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn是为地球人制造的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不知道它蕴藏着怎样的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能做的只有守望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候已久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天没有发动零时空间…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何又陷入了沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是你在为我做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.97,0:22:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆日死之巫女吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:23:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放逐时代的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.78,0:24:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三台同时袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.43,0:24:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方和和子约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.56,0:24:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.29,0:24:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.66,0:24:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要一口气看完啊
